ENTRY            F0730   20251225   20260311   20260311       F107
SUBENT        F0730001   20251225   20260311   20260311       F107
BIB                 11         42
TITLE      Level densities of the Ni-59 nuclei
AUTHOR     (B.V.Zhuravlev)
INSTITUTE  (4RUSFEI)
REFERENCE  (J,BAS,64,331,2000)  English transl. of IZV,64,414
           (J,IZV,64,414,2000) - data at 12.3, 16.3, 18.3 MeV
            Data at 26.6 MeV presented on fig. 2 and data at
            26.8 MeV presented in A0276014 are the same.
           ((S,ISINN-5,247,1997)=(S,JINR-E3-97-213,247,1997)) -
                 same data at 16.3 MeV
           (J,IZV,62,110,1998) - data at 12.3, 16.3 and 18.3 MeV
           (J,BAS,62,93,1998)   English transl. of IZV,62,110
           (J,IZV,63,959,1999) - same data at 12.3 and 16.3 MeV
           (J,BAS,63,764,1999) Engl. transl. of IZV,63,959
           ((S,ISINN-6,151,1998)=(S,JINR-E3-98-202,151,1998)) -
             same dataset as in IZV,63,959,1999
REL-REF    (O,F1084001,B.V.Zhuravlev+,S,ISINN-16,237,2009) -
                             additional data at 12.3 and 16.3 MeV
           (O,A0276001,N.S.Birjukov+,C,83KIEV,3,290,1983) -
                                                 data at 26.8 MeV
           (O,A0832007,B.V.Zhuravlev+,S,ISINN-6,151,1998) - Level
                                               density presented.
FACILITY   (VDGT,3CPRAEP) HI-13
DETECTOR   (SCIN) Three scintillation detectors (diam. 10.5 cm and
           5 cm thickness) and photomultiplier XP-2041 were
           placed at the flight distances of 6.1, 6.55 and 5.15 m.
SAMPLE     Self-supporting metal foil with the thickness of
           0.592 mg/cm2 was used as a target.
METHOD     (TOF)
ANALYSIS   Neutron spectra were measured at the angles of 20,30,
           40,60,70,80,100,110,120,140,150,160 degr. Spectra and
           angular distributions were integrated over an angle.
HISTORY    (20060719C)
           (20090615A) New REFERENCE code was added.
           (20100125A) New REFERENCE code was added.
           (20111215A) Subent 5 was added. New REFERENCE code was
                       added.
           (20130204A) New REFERENCE code was added.
           (20140312A) SD: Ref. IZV,63 added. Subent 5 deleted -
           duplication with part of the data presented in Subent 3
           Subent 4 deleted (duplication with A0276.019)
           REACTION code in Subent 3 corrected.
           (20251225U) SD: Small corrections in all Subents.
ENDBIB              42
NOCOMMON             0          0
ENDSUBENT           45
